What is SPECKit??

SPECKit Plus ek AI-centric development framework hai jo software creation ke process ko structured 
aur streamlined banata hai. Ismein project ko five clear phases mein  divided kiya jaata hai:
Constitution, Specify, Plan, Tasks, aur Implement. Yeh phases humein step-by-step guidance dete hain, taake final
product speed, accuracy, aur business needs ke exactly according to develop ho.

1. Constitution 

Constitution phase project ki bunyaad hota hai. Is stage mein project ka asli maqsad, goals, stakeholders, value, aur boundaries
define ki jati hain. Yeh phase ensure karta hai ke poori team ko exactly maloom ho ke hum kya bana rahe hain aur kis liye. Yahan se sab kuch
shuru hota hai aur direction milti hai.

2. Specify 

Specify phase mein project ki saaf aur mukammal requirements likhi jati hain. Yahan functional aur non-functional requirements, user stories,
scenarios, aur expected outcomes sab tafseel se define kiye jate hain. Isse project ke tamam features bilkul wazeh ho jate hain. Confusion khatam 
hoti hai aur clarity aati hai.

3. Plan 

Plan phase mein requirements ko dekhte huye development ka mukammal roadmap tayyar kiya jata hai. Isme timeline, milestones, resources, risks aur completion
strategy decide hoti hai. Yeh phase project ko organized, structured aur time-bound banata hai. Har step ka proper schedule ban jata 

4. Tasks 

Tasks phase mein planning ko chhote aur actionable steps mein tod diya jata hai. Har task ke inputs, outputs, dependencies aur priority wazeh define hoti hai.
Is stage mein development ka actual workflow design hota hai. Kaam manageable aur trackable ban jata hai.

5. Implement 

Implement phase asli coding ya building phase hota hai. Yahan hum tasks follow karte huye system banate hain, test karte hain aur ensure karte 
hain ke product plan ke mutabiq kaam kar raha ho. Yeh phase final working software ya product deliver karta hai. Yahan planning reality mein badal jati hai.
